1st Occurrence within Subject Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL= "Y") after sorting for USUBJID and AE start time (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occurrence of SOC Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") within each body system or organ class (AEBODSYS) after sorting by USUBJID, AEBODSYS, and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occurrence of Preferred Term Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") within equal dictionary-derived terms (AEDECOD) after sorting by USUBJID, AEBODSYS, AEDECOD and  AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Max Sev./Int. Occurrence Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") after sorting by USUBJID, descending AE severity (AESEV), and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Max Sev./Int. Occur Within SOC Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") within each body system or organ class (AEBODSYS) after sorting by USUBJID, AEBODSYS, descending AE severity (AESEV), and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Max Sev./Int. Occur Within PT Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") within equal dictionary-derived terms (AEDECOD) after sorting by USUBJID, AEBODSYS, AEDECOD, descending AE severity (AESEV), and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occurrence of Related TEAE Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE related to study treatment of the subject  (TRTEMFL = "Y" and AEREL="RELATED") after sorting by USUBJID and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occurrence of Serious TEAE Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first serious treatment-emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y" and AESER = "Y") after sorting by USUBJID and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occurrence of Rel. Serious TEAE Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first serious treatment-emergent AE related to study treatment of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y", AESER = "Y", AEREL = "RELATED") after sorting  by USUBJID and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occur of TEAE Lead to Disc. IP Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE leading to discontinuation of study treatment of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y" and AEACN = "WITHDRAWN") after sorting by USUBJID and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occur of TEAE Leading to Disc. Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE  leading to discontinuation of study participation of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y" and AECAUDIS = "Y") after sorting by USUBJID and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occur of Rel. and Lead to Disc. Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent and treatment-related AE leading to discontinuation of study participation of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y", AEREL = "RELATED" and AECAUDIS = "Y") after sorting by USUBJID and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occurrence of Fatal TEAE Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first fatal treatment-emergent AE  of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y" and AEOUT = "FATAL") after sorting by USUBJID and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occur of Fatal and Related TEAE Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first fatal treatment-emergent AE related to study treatment of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y", AEOUT = "FATAL" and AEREL = "RELATED") after sorting by USUBJD and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occurrence of Max Related TEAE Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") after sorting by USUBJID, descending  relationship (AEREL), and AE start datetime (ASTDTC).

label: 1st Occur of Max Rel. Within SOC Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") within each body system or organ class (AEBODSYS) after sorting by USUBJID, AEBODSYS, descending relationship (AEREL), and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

label: 1st Occur of Max Rel. Within PT Flag
method: Set to "Y" for the first treatment-emergent AE of the subject (TRTEMFL = "Y") within equal dictionary-derived terms (AEDECOD) after sorting by USUBJID, AEBODSYS, AEDECOD, descending AE relationshiü (AEREL), and AE start datetime (ASTDTM)

Analysis Date
method: Date part of EG.EGDTC converted to numeric SAS date

label: Analysis Time
method: Time part of EG.EGDTC converted to numeric SAS time

label: Analysis Datetime
method: EG.EGDTC converted to numeric SAS date

label: Analysis Relative Day
method: If ADT >= TRTSDT then ADY = ADT - TRTSDT + 1. Else if ADT<TRTSDT then ADY = ADT - TRTSDT

label: Analysis Visit
method: If ADTM <= TRTSDTM then AVISIT = "Baseline". Else if EG.VISIT="TREATMENT" then AVISIT = "Treatment". Else AVISIT = "DAY XX" with XX being the prescribed study day of EG.VISIT

label: Analysis Timepoint
method: If VISITNUM=1 then ATPT = "Pre-dose". Else if EG.EGTPT="60 MIN" then ATPT = "1 hour". Else if EG.EGTPT ^= MISSING then ATPT = lowcase(EG.EGTPT).
VARIABLE_CODELIST: Pre-dose@30 min@1 hour@2 hours@4 hours@8 hours@12 hours@24 hours@48 hours

label: Analysis Timepoint Reference
method: If EG.EGTPTREF="START OF EXPOSURE TO STUDY DRUG" or VISITNUM=1  then ATPTREF = "Start of exposure". Else if EG.EGTPTREF="END OF EXPOSURE TO STUDY DRUG" then ATPTREF = "End of exposure"

label: Anchor Timepoint for Analysis Rel. Time
method: If EG.EGTPTREF="START OF TREATMENT" or VISITNUM=1 then ARFTDTM = TRTSDTM. Else if EG.EGTPTREF="END OF TREATMENT" then ARFTDTM = TRTEDTM

label: Analysis Relative Time
method: ARELTM = ADTM - ARFTDTM

label: Attended Screening Visit (Day 1)
method: Set to "Y" if SV.VISITNUM=1 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING, "N" otherwise.

label: Attended Treatment Visit (Day 1 to 3)
method: Set to "Y" if SV.VISITNUM=2 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING, "N" otherwise.

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 8)
method: Set to "Y" if SV.VISITNUM=3 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING, "N" otherwise.

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 15)
method: If SV.VISITNUM=4 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING then ATTFUD15 = "Y". Else if DM.COHORT="COHORT1 (INTRAVENOUS)" then ATTFUD15 = "NA". Else ATTFUD15 = "N".

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 22)
method: If SV.VISITNUM=5 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING then ATTFUD22 = "Y". Else if DM.COHORT IN ("COHORT1 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT2 (INTRAVENOUS)") then ATTFUD22 = "NA". Else ATTFUD22 = "N".

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 29)
method: If SV.VISITNUM=6 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING then ATTFUD29 = "Y". Else if DM.COHORT IN ("COHORT1 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT2 (INTRAVENOUS)") then ATTFUD29 = "NA". Else ATTFUD29 = "N".

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 43)
method: If SV.VISITNUM=7 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING then ATTFUD43 = "Y". Else if DM.COHORT IN ("COHORT1 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT2 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT3 (INTRAVENOUS)") then ATTFUD43 = "NA". Else ATTFUD43 = "N".

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 57)
method: If SV.VISITNUM=8 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING then ATTFUD57 = "Y". Else if DM.COHORT IN ("COHORT1 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT2 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT3 (INTRAVENOUS)") then ATTFUD57 = "NA". Else ATTFUD57 = "N".

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 71)
method: If SV.VISITNUM=9 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING  or VISITNUM=98 then ATTFUD71 = "Y". Else if DM.COHORT IN ("COHORT1 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT2 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT3 (INTRAVENOUS)"  "COHORT4 (INTRAVENOUS)") then ATTFUD71 = "NA". Else ATTFUD71 = "N".

label: Attended Follow-Up Visit (Day 85)
method: If SV.VISITNUM=10 and SV.SVSTDTC^=MISSING then ATTFUD85 = "Y". Else if DM.COHORT IN ("COHORT1 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT2 (INTRAVENOUS)" "COHORT3 (INTRAVENOUS)"  "COHORT4 (INTRAVENOUS)") then ATTFUD85 = "NA". Else ATTFUD85 = "N".
